      <section name='doll'>

         <para number='1' comment='Get doll'>
         Ivan frowns at you and tells you that you can't just take one of the dolls - you will have to buy one.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Buy doll - already got one'>
         Ivan frowns in distress, and says, "I am sorry my friend, but the authorities have restricted the sale of the Famous Figures of Federation dolls to just one per customer. So I cannot sell you another."
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Not enough groats'>
         I am sorry friend," says Ivan, "but I have to feed my family, so I can't just give the dolls away. Come back when you have 100 groats for me."
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Sell the player a doll'>
         Ivan grins happily and says, "But of course comrade, I would be more than happy to sell you one of my beautiful dolls." He takes one down from the shelf and hands it to you. In return, you pay the 100 groats.
         </para>

