      <section name='dolldiesel'>

         <para number='1' comment='Shake Diesel doll - full'>
         You shake the doll and hear a hollow rattle as something inside it moves about. Examining the doll, you find a seam between the top and bottom halves.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Shake Diesel doll - empty'>
         You shake the Diesel doll but it doesn't make any sound.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Open Diesel doll - full'>
         You twist the Diesel doll and the top pops off, revealing a smaller doll inside it! You remove the other doll, which is painted with Selena of the Spaceways' face, and close the Diesel doll again.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Open Diesel doll - empty'>
         You open up the Diesel doll, but there is nothing inside it, so you close it again.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Drop Diesel doll'>
         You drop the Diesel doll. It lands with a thump, and the wood smashes into several pieces. The face seems to look up at you reproachfully... an efficient cleaning droid clears up the mess and vanishes again.
         </para>

